Maven:

	1. Read POM.xml
	2. Downloads dependencies into local repo
	3. Executes life cycles build phases and/or goals
	4. Execute Plugins

All executed according to selected build profile

Maven Reads pom.xml -> Maven Local Repository
	1. Build Life Cycles
		a. Phases
			i. Goals
	2. Dependencies (JARs)
	3. Build Plugins
	4. Build Profiles
		
